PrecisAmendments to the IMMIGRATION REGULATIONS, 1978 - Phase II (in consequence of Bill C-86 affecting most areas of the Immigration Program) allowing to more effectively select and process those who come to Canada, improving the level of service, better protecting Canadian society by tightening up enforcement and control measures, and streamlining the refugee determination system, effective August 9, 1993.

precis:
Amendments to the IMMIGRATION REGULATIONS, 1978 - Phase II (in consequence
of Bill C-86 affecting most areas of the Immigration Program) allowing
to more effectively select and process those who come to Canada, improving
the level of service, better protecting Canadian society by tightening up
enforcement and control measures, and streamlining the refugee
determination system, effective August 9, 1993.
